**Simplified Text:**

I love collecting things. Many people enjoy collecting, and one in three adults does it too. It is a world of passion, envy and enthusiasm. If you want to start collecting, remember one thing: you should only collect things that you love. People have been collecting things since the beginning of time. They collect stones, seashells, flowers, paintings and other things. I have been collecting all my life. I have collected everything from flowers to pottery and paintings. My first collection was of stones picked up in my parents' garden. I was fascinated by these objects. I am not alone in being interested in collecting objects. One in three adults indulges the same passion. There are many reasons why people collect. For me, it's just something I enjoy doing. You do not have to be rich and powerful to start a collection. You can collect items as different as tulip bulbs and china cups. As small objects become a popular collector's item, they begin to rise in price.<eos>
